<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Estoffe - Seu Carrinho</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col pt-24">

    <main class="flex-grow max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <div class="mb-8">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-green-700 block mb-2">Sacola de Compras</span>
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light tracking-tight text-gray-900">Seu <span class="font-extrabold">Carrinho</span></h1>
            <div class="w-12 h-[2px] bg-green-700 mt-3"></div>
        </div>

        <% if (produtosNoCarrinho.length === 0) { %>
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-sm p-12 text-center shadow-sm max-w-md mx-auto my-12">
                <div class="text-gray-300 text-6xl mb-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-cart-x"></i>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Seu carrinho está vazio</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">Que tal navegar pelo catálogo e escolher uma peça exclusiva de alta tapeçaria?</p>
                <a href="/produtos" class="inline-block bg-green-950 hover:bg-green-800 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-6 py-3 rounded-sm transition duration-300">
                    Ver Produtos
                </a>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">
                
                <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-4">
                    <% produtosNoCarrinho.forEach(item => { %>
                        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 p-4 rounded-sm shadow-sm flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4 transition hover:shadow-md">
                            
                            <img src="../<%= item.imagem %>" alt="<%= item.nome %>" class="w-24 h-24 object-cover rounded-sm bg-gray-50">
                            
                            <div class="flex-grow text-center sm:text-left">
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-base"><%= item.nome %></h3>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5">Código: #<%= item.codProduto %></p>
                                <p class="text-green-800 font-semibold text-sm mt-2">R$ <%= item.preco.toLocaleString('pt-BR', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 w-full sm:w-auto justify-between sm:justify-end">
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-sm">
                                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 mr-1">Qtd:</span> <strong class="font-bold"><%= item.quantidade %></strong>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="text-right min-w-[90px]">
                                    <span class="block text-xs text-gray-400">Subtotal</span>
                                    <span class="font-extrabold text-gray-900 text-sm">R$ <%= item.subtotal.toLocaleString('pt-BR', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></span>
                                </div>

                                <form action="/carrinho/remover/<%= item.codProduto %>" method="POST" class="inline">
                                    <button type="submit" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-600 p-2 transition" title="Remover item">
                                        <i class="bi bi-trash3 text-lg"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </form>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    <% }) %>

                    <div class="pt-2">
                        <a href="/produtos" class="text-sm text-green-800 hover:text-green-950 font-medium inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Continuar comprando
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 p-6 rounded-sm shadow-md space-y-6 lg:sticky lg:top-28">
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 border-b border-gray-100 pb-3">Resumo do Pedido</h2>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-600">
                            <span>Subtotal dos itens</span>
                            <span>R$ <%= total.toLocaleString('pt-BR', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-gray-600">
                            <span>Entrega / Frete</span>
                            <span class="text-green-700 font-medium">Grátis</span>
                        </div>
                        <hr class="border-gray-100 my-2">
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-base font-bold text-gray-900 pt-2">
                            <span>Total Estimado</span>
                            <span class="text-xl text-green-950">R$ <%= total.toLocaleString('pt-BR', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <form action="/pedido/finalizar" method="POST" class="pt-2">
                        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-green-950 hover:bg-green-800 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-sm transition duration-300 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs flex items-center justify-center gap-2 cursor-pointer shadow-sm">
                            <i class="bi bi-credit-card mr-1"></i> Finalizar Pedido
                        </button>
                    </form>
                    
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-400 text-center leading-relaxed">
                        Ao finalizar, seu pedido será enviado para o painel de produção da Estoffe. O pagamento e detalhes de entrega serão combinados diretamente com a nossa equipe.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        <% } %>
    </main>

</body>
</html>